His fingers have nodules.

582
00:32:18,543 --> 00:32:20,311
I think his doctors misdiagnosed him.

583
00:32:20,378 --> 00:32:22,813
Or you sprinkled too much
wishful thinking in your tea.

584
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:24,781
Obese man with lung cancer...

585
