for his heart failure.

586
00:32:26,851 --> 00:32:29,019
Nodules can mean something
else, something curable.

587
00:32:29,087 --> 00:32:30,720
Go back to the e.r.

588
00:32:30,788 --> 00:32:32,689
My thanks to you and your cold feet.

589
00:32:32,757 --> 00:32:34,558
What's going on?

590
00:32:34,625 --> 00:32:36,093
