What is she hiding?

662
00:35:52,463 --> 00:35:53,963
You don't know...

663
00:35:54,031 --> 00:35:56,198
either we have all the
clues and we're idiots

664
00:35:56,266 --> 00:35:57,534
or we don't have all the clues.

665
00:35:57,601 --> 00:36:02,104
Possible exposure, people, places.

666
00:36:02,172 --> 00:36:03,840
Both.

667
00:36:07,578 --> 00:36:08,912
Bad lie.

668
00:36:08,979 --> 00:36:11,414
Did you really think
the beaches in hawaii

